CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 14, 1963, reads: "DOING THE CAN-CAN - In authentic Parisian costumes of black velvet and red satin, with black velvet bonnets trimmed with white plumes, this line stopped the show. Starring in chorus were (left to right) Mildred Bass, Alma Fox, Helen Horsley, Elaine Courtney, Frances Nunn, Norma Malone, Evelyn Anderson, Roberta Watson, and Lois Watson."
TitMainTitle: Members of Junior Mothers wearing Parisian dance costumes dancing the can-can, including Mildred Bass, Alma Speed Fox, Helen Horsely, Elaine Courtney, Frances Bell Nunn, Norma Malone, Evelyn Anderson, Roberta Watson, and Lois Weaver Watson, at Hilton Hotel
